    "At this search stage, it produced 3108 article titles containing the keywords we had defined.",
    "A search of the ACM digital library returned 628 titles, IEEExplore 473 titles, ScienceDirect 721 titles, and Springer 1286 titles.",
    "RQ1 and RQ2 identify published journals and productive authors contributing to NER research.",
    "RQ3-RQ5 discusses preprocessing, datasets, and NER application domains, RQ6-RQ8 discusses techniques feature extraction, NER approach, and method, and RQ9 identifies NER evaluation techniques.",
